<D>__{here they are, captain.}
<A>__{the "captain" turns from a monitor: it's sidney.}
<C>__{sidney}
<D>__{just give me one goad reason mister bond, from lloyds of london why i shouldn't kill both of you, burn your boat, and use your bodies for shark bait.}
<C>__{wade}
<P>__{(chirping up)}
<D>__{so you two know each other!?! small world, ain't it? what happened? commitment problems?}
