<D>__{every wharf rat from here to hong kong knows what's on that boat and i'm claiming it. one third of that gold is mine.}
<C>__{bond}
<D>__{that's fine, but even a little london girl knows that one third of nothing is still nothing.}
<A>__{there's a flicker of doubt in her eyes. she turns to taro:}
<C>__{sidney}
<D>__{was he carrying anything?}
<A>__{taro holds up the bond's diving belt, indicating 'nothing'. angrily:}
<C>__{sidney}
<D>__{search him.}
<A>__{the men look at bond wearing only swim trunks. nobody moves.}
